lead_paragraph: Ariya Jutanugarn held on for her first L.P.G.A. Tour title, closing with a one-under-par 71 at the Yokohama Tire L.P.G.A. Classic in Prattville, Ala.

headline.main: Ariya Jutanugarn Wins First L.P.G.A. Title
